metadata.name: ✨VIZ, Starjester
metadata.description:
She is a burning shooting star, and she knows what you wished. The brighter the dream, the hotter ✨VIZ is — as if she were a shard of the ☀️Sun. You want to catch and hold her, but be careful not to burn yourself!

aoibluevi, 2021
2400 x 3000 pixels, 60 fps, original soundtrack
